			"value": "<p><em>Weapon (@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-equipment.Item.pM8eu7VlKCHmEi3N]{Javelin}) - Uncommon</em></p><p><em>Javelins are long, thin spears. They can be used for thrusting attacks, but are designed to be thrown great distances.</em></p><p>When you hit with this magic weapon, you can choose for it to deal Lightning damage instead of Piercing.</p><p><strong>Action</strong> - 120 ft. Line (5 ft. wide) - 1/Dawn</p><p>[[/save DEX 13]]{DC 13 Dexterity Save}</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure: </strong>Targets take[[/damage 4d6 Lightning]].</p></li><li><p><strong>Success: </strong>Half damage.</p></li></ul><p>Properties:</p><p>&amp;reference[magic weapon], &amp;Reference[Thrown] (30/120), &amp;Reference[Retain]</p><section class=\"secret\" id=\"foundry-secret-1\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The <strong>Attack</strong> activity lets you pick Lightning or Piercing damage and remembers your last choice.</p></section>",
